=== Main festivals ===
* Annual festival ({{ill|lt=April 29|Q2535|qid=Q2535|1=April 29}})

=== Local information ===
* Nahaka Shrine (Lower Shrine): Noka 1-8-1, Ōtsu, Shiga
* Nahaka Aramitama Shrine (Upper Shrine): Noka 1-9-14, Ōtsu, Shiga

; Access
* Rail: JR West {{ill|lt=Kosei Line|Q599974|qid=Q599974|1=Kosei Line}}, {{ill|lt=Ogoto-Onsen Station|Q5367599|qid=Q5367599|1=Ogoto-onsen Station}} or {{ill|lt=Hieizan-Sakamoto Station|Q5367380|qid=Q5367380|1=Hieizan Sakamoto Station}} (about 15 min walk)
* Bus: from {{ill|lt=Biwako-Hamaotsu Station|Q5644181|qid=Q5644181|1=Biwako-Hamaōtsu Station}} by {{ill|lt=Kojaku Kōtsū|Q11551295|qid=Q11551295|1=Kojak Bus}} bus (to Katata), get off at “Noka,” then 3 min walk

